Nahetuduka
Ācayagāmittika
Pañhāvāra
Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Nahetuduka
75.
1652Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe satta, adhipatiyā dasa, anantare cha, samanantare cha, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe tīṇi, nissaye terasa, upanissaye nava, purejāte tīṇi, pacchājāte tīṇi, āsevane tīṇi, kamme satta, vipāke ekaṃ, āhāre satta, indriye jhāne magge satta, sampayutte tīṇi, vippayutte pañca, atthiyā terasa, natthiyā cha, vigate cha, avigate terasa. (Evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)
1653Paccanīyānulomaṃ.
1654Ācayagāmittikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.
